{"type":"message","id":"4888a64a","parentId":"235a9b4b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:14:34.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have both the pulse log and the pulse output. Let me summarize what happened.\n\nThe pulse log was from 19:03:47 (7:03 PM ET). The pulse that just ran was at 19:13:49 (7:13 PM ET).\n\nFrom the pulse output:\n1. It detected the TIC experiment needs a classifier implementation\n2. It applied a mutation creating `scripts/tic_classifier.ps1` \n3. It also created `scripts/test-tic.ps1`\n4. It committed changes to git\n5. A new proposed mutation was created for the next pulse\n\nThe mutation was applied to create the TIC classifier script.","thinkingSignature":"e62ff4c2ff2a450bbe69c2951a3f99ddf7adb2751ce9544328634fe201b152d3"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse Summary — 2026-03-23 19:13 UTC**\n\n**What ran:** TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier implementation.\n\n**Observation:** The TIC experiment — testing whether causal structure equals invariant structure — was stalled without a concrete implementation. The pulse detected this gap and initiated the classifier.\n\n**Mutation applied:** Created `scripts/tic_classifier.ps1` — a PowerShell script that:\n- Classifies pulse log lines as **INVARIANT** (persistent across cycles: goals, architecture docs, phase markers) vs **VARIANT** (ephemeral: timestamps, observations, mutations)\n- Uses pattern matching against known invariant/variant regexes\n- Measures invariant ratio across all pulse logs\n- Predicts next-pulse content from accumulated invariants and scores prediction accuracy\n\n**Also created:** `scripts/test-tic.ps1`\n\n**Git commit:** `938a7d1` — 9 files changed, +412/-111 lines.\n\n**Status:** TIC classifier is ready. Next pulse should run the test script and validate against success criteria (>70% classification accuracy, >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy).\n\n**Proposed mutation waiting:** 1 (likely the next TIC test/validation step)"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2083,"output":390,"cacheRead":11887,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14360,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774307659663}}
